data.eml:eml: Ten new species of Cephennula Jałoszyński (Coleoptera, Staphylinidae, Scydmaeninae) from Malaysia

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Jałoszyński, Paweł (2011): Ten new species of Cephennula Jałoszyński (Coleoptera, Staphylinidae, Scydmaeninae) from Malaysia. Zootaxa 3113: 36-52, DOI: 10.5281/zenodo.279337
